# Task 5 â€“ Student Management System

-> Description
This is a Student Management System developed using Java.

The system allows users to:
- Add students
- Remove students
- Search students
- Edit student details
- Display all students
- Save and load data from file

->Features
- Menu-driven interface
- File handling (data persistence)
- Input validation
- CRUD operations
- Automatic data loading on restart

->Technologies Used
- Java
- ArrayList
- File Handling (BufferedReader, FileWriter)
- Object-Oriented Programming


